Package: shinyStan
Title: Explore Your MCMC
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Jonah Gabry <jsg2201@columbia.edu> [aut, cre]",
    "Stan Development Team [aut]",
    "Michael Andreae [ctb]",
    "Yuanjun Gao [ctb]",
    "Dongying Song [ctb]"
  ))
Maintainer: Jonah Gabry <jsg2201@columbia.edu>
Description: Explore MCMC output through interactive visualizations and tables
    using the Shiny web application framework. The ShinyStan app is run 
    locally, but the package also provides a function that enables users to 
    easily deploy their own ShinyStan apps online using RStudio's ShinyApps 
    service (to deploy an app users must install the suggested shinyapps package,
    which is available from RStudio. See Additional_repositories.).
URL: http://mc-stan.org, https://github.com/stan-dev/shinystan 
BugReports: https://github.com/stan-dev/shinystan/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.1),
    ggplot2 (>= 1.0.0),
    shiny (>= 0.11.2)
License: GPL (>=3)
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    rstan,
    coda,
    knitr (>= 1.9),
